      "paragraph_name": "STEP0",
      "summary": null,
      "purpose": "This step executes the IEFBR14 program, a dummy program that performs no actual processing. In this JCL, it's used to delete the existing VSAM datasets AWS.M2.CARDDEMO.PAUTDB.ROOT.FILEO and AWS.M2.CARDDEMO.PAUTDB.CHILD.FILEO. The DD statements DD1 and DD2 define these datasets with a DISP=(OLD,DELETE,DELETE) parameter, ensuring they are deleted at the end of the step. This step prepares the environment for the subsequent step, which will create new versions of these datasets with the unloaded data.",
